    <section class="about-us">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Job Portal</h2>
            <p>An online job portal is a dynamic platform that revolutionizes the way job seekers and employers connect in the digital age. 
               It serves as a comprehensive database where job vacancies and candidate profiles are showcased, facilitating a seamless recruitment process. 
               For job seekers, these portals provide access to a wide array of job listings across various industries and locations, allowing users to filter
               and find opportunities that match their skills, experience, and career aspirations. Advanced features like resume building tools, 
               job alerts, and career resources empower candidates to present themselves effectively and stay informed about new openings..</p>

            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <p>The mission of an online job portal is to seamlessly connect job seekers with employers, providing a user-friendly platform for discovering 
                and applying to job opportunities. It aims to streamline the recruitment process, ensuring efficiency and accessibility for all users. Ultimately,
                it strives to empower individuals and organizations to achieve their career and hiring goals with ease and transparency.</p>
    </section>

